data.description: This home is move in ready, on a mature well treed quiet lot completely landscaped, gently lived in. Central location lots of privacy, backed onto a Nature Park. Spacious interior offers a beautiful Kitchen, granite countertops, Pantry and Island. Laundry room off kitchen has Washer/Dryer and Wine Cooler. Recessed Ceiling details, California Shutters, French Doors in the main living area add to the charm. Primary bedroom ensuite has soaker tub and separate Shower, walk-in closet ,double vanity with access to the enclosed Patio. The yard has covered entertainment area complete with TV screen ,refrigerator, shutters and Hot Tub. Deer Proof Garden area. Double Garage Floor offers Central Air and Heat with new finished Floor. Tool Shed out Front to store equipment,Lawn mower included. Enjoy all Rockport has to offer at your fingertips, Shopping ,Restaurants, Arts, Beach ,Fishing and more! Entertain or Relax with family and Friends in this inviting Home. Call for your appointment Today.
